撚圾！係垃圾之中既垃圾！含家產之中既含家產，屌你老母，鳩硬真係無親戚，男人唔叫雞唔去滾既全部都要死全家，著polo反領既都係冚家剷！冇翻幾萬蚊喺銀包好死撚咗佢啦，唔撚係男人黎！額頭有綠光，個仔做奴隸! 個女去做雞! 仲要係至撚cheap果隻雞! $100幫人含撚奶屎眼中出！屌你老母，我係人中之龍，你係乜撚野呀 ？你就係冇家教既冚家剷，死左就要落地獄，唉屌休息啊食飛煙先，好眼訓，<span style=\"color: red;\">一陣起身係個被竇暖粒粒，望一望下面暖暖地，見到大波驊幫你含緊</span>，真係含得撚橡皮糖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://thumbs.gfycat.com%2FGrossThoughtfulHoneycreeper-size_restricted.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n做你老母中國人<br />\n邋遢又冇品真正賤民<br />\n到處罪惡貪官<br />\n永冇認錯檢討<br />\n閪吱閪冧<br />\n<br />\n做你老母中國人<br />\n賤嘢就最醒欺騙別人<br />\n佢係最貪心<br />\n佢仲更痴根<br />\n相當黑暗<br />\n<br />\n做你老母中國人<br />\n賤嘢就最叻諉過別人<br />\n著嘅用嘅賓週<br />\n喝嘅食嘅碌鳩<br />\n等緊支爆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/uGFVRdt.gif\" />"},{"pid":"7d42912873563fe1ef19ecf89ffc4a18d956860b","tid":1789850,"uid":75684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"又比曱大大氣功醫好左,一定係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68792eff1b3c7d28233b174eb7eb93eb1b581c15","tid":1789850,"uid":314083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ad73588f73b2f8a0fab764716f41ede705b25fc","tid":1789850,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"【習近平慰問鄭若驊傷勢 鄭若驊：像香港一樣會好起來】<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平下午在澳門會見出席慶祝澳門回歸20周年活動的行政長官林鄭月娥，以及部分政府官員。<br />\n<br />\n習近平表示，中央充分肯定林鄭月娥在非常時期，展現出的勇氣與擔當，指林鄭月娥到北京述職時，提出特區政府下一步工作的設想，中央完全支持，希望特區政府各個部門繼續在行政長官領導下，各司其職，密切配合，形成合力，共同將香港的事情辦好。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥感謝習近平接見，表示一定會帶領特區政府，繼續做好止暴制亂工作，盡快恢復香港社會秩序。她又與習近平握手，並向對方表示經港珠澳大橋抵達澳門，又逐一介紹隨行官員。<br />\n<br />\n習近平問候早前在英國跌傷手的律政司司長鄭若驊；她感謝習近平的關心，指自己的身體「就像香港一樣，一定會好起來」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2489619137984983/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2489619137984983%2F&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=196d24eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2489619137984983/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"刁西真係望之不似人君。笑容尷尷尬尬咁。應該係亡国君。"},{"pid":"ff7869959732ffa9c3452d4813a4b8cbe93f9a3e","tid":1789850,"uid":136147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ed50df4811a694cc27c07e27048622aad6c4522","tid":1789850,"uid":232594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e217b5eab3d9c0842f22f79002a3fe35f8fc2eca","tid":1789850,"uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cj0WDJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCj0WDJb.png&h=2ad8a5b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"成班奴才咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"成班太監咁 終於明咩叫陪笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbd43f74d785a75db419b273fdc1ddecf689800","tid":1789850,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新增挪威文 英日法西文tweet整合<br />\n<br />\n快做各國文宣Twitter<br />\n<br />\n告知國際政府 社會<br />\n英文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2S47d4V\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S47d4V&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=70dc1984\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2S47d4V</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjPPXte.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjPPXte.png&h=aa7e36a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSolomon yue <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1207639630994034694?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1207639630994034694%3Fs%3D21&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=007b8d9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomon